{"tid":949677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭民望挫　鄭若驊三司包尾","createTime":"2018-12-21T03:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T05:20:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"37f913bd57bda05b7a7071188176b682808c5147","tid":949677,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:37:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181221/20573762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F20573762&d=K1xDqp88wxMF2YPk1dXPKcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=4a3470a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F20573762&h=21f88808\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181221/20573762</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月21日 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭民望挫　鄭若驊三司包尾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181221/large/21la6p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181221%2Flarge%2F21la6p04.jpg&h=5af276c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊<br />\n<br />\n【中大民調】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】被國家主席習近平讚賞「志不求易，事不避難」的特首林鄭月娥，其民望卻未獲香港人肯定，根據中文大學亞太研究所的調查顯示，林鄭、被傳或被撤換的政務司司長張建宗、財政司司長陳茂波，三人評分較去年同期顯著下跌，年輕、學歷高的市民，給予官員評分則相對其他組別較低。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181221/large/a1003a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181221%2Flarge%2Fa1003a.gif&h=6604896d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張建宗陳茂波評分續跌<br />\n<br />\n中文大學香港亞太研究所本月11至17日晚上透過電話進行調查，成功訪問708名18歲或以上的市民，調查中途才爆出律政司以證據不足為由，不檢控收取UGL巨額款項的前特首梁振英。<br />\n<br />\n市民對林鄭月娥的整體表現最新評分，由去年12月的56分，下跌3.3分，至本月的52.7分。有傳林鄭想撤換的張建宗，整體表現評分由去年12月的52.9分，下跌2.9分，至本月的50分。而陳茂波整體表現評分，由去年12月的46.3分，下跌3.1分，至本月的43.2分。<br />\n<br />\n至於決定不起訴梁振英的律政司司長鄭若驊，整體表現最新評分由今年1月（調查於今年才開始為鄭進行民望評分）的38.9分，升至本月的39.3分，微升0.4分。<br />\n<br />\n調查分析受訪者背景，發現51歲或以上、學歷為小學或以下和自稱中上層或上層的受訪市民，給予官員的評分較其他組別高；相反，30歲或以下、學歷達大專或以上，和自稱下層或中下層的受訪市民，給予官員評分則相對較低。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姚國雄  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n大律師公會主席：律政司長需負責<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n西環集中營：美調整對港政策非靠嚇 (季陶)"},{"pid":"92fa255748869d57d462c12c9c89c67e1ce23f47","tid":949677,"uid":216817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cd1f1c69540c6f7be83ac0b27d303cd771b7f6d","tid":949677,"uid":47422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"51歲或以上<br />\n30歲或以下<br />\n中間啲人死晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f781e794a7182650b48a1a457756047655000fa","tid":949677,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:36:28.000Z","msg":"到底點先可以畀到40以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5707891ae06f84adee9e2370f8170634f65f9dfd","tid":949677,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"講真啲分低到落地核又點"},{"pid":"771aad012095b41e99d6841072f084219eb5b8ec","tid":949677,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"浮雲"},{"pid":"f37b55cae0dee537132d5eca53333ee8a23ae9c7","tid":949677,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"呢班廢柴都視民望如糞土㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fdc0551f346e00d4edd01cc2236f4888d7e9ae","tid":949677,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"選舉制度係向選民負責 你班蟻民都唔係投票個班 民望跌關佢撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be710cb29641b01f23fa61b2ea853d6e90dd4df2","tid":949677,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0